WHEREAS, she is the cherished daughter of Rusty and Cheré Daigle and the proud
older sister of Savannah, whose love and support have helped guide her accomplishments.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Olivia Daigle on being crowned the 2025–2026
Louisiana State Queen Sugar, and does honor her for her grace, leadership, and service and
extends best wishes for a successful and impactful reign.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Olivia Daigle and her family as an expression of the Senate's esteem, appreciation, and best
wishes for continued success.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
